title: Personal income in Florida - income per capita 2000 to 2018
summary: The chart at hand is a line chart where the x axis denotes Year and a y axis denotes Income in U.S. dollars. In total the number of data points it has is 19.
Overall Income in U.S. dollars has increased over the Year.
The most drastic decrease took place within the Year '08 and '09.
Maximum Income in U.S. dollars, about 50070.0 was reported at Year '18
The lowest Income in U.S. dollars, of value 29428.0 was reported at Year '00
